---
title: Syntax Highlighting
meta_title: Pyro &mdash; Syntax Highlighting
---

The Pyro GitHub repository contains a syntax-highlighting file for Vim, `etc/pyro.vim`.

Copy the `etc/pyro.vim` file to your `~/.vim/syntax/` directory to enable syntax highlighting for Pyro in Vim, e.g.

::: code
    cp ./etc/pyro.vim ~/.vim/syntax/
